10:50.598 --> 10:52.098
How come?

10:52.100 --> 10:55.271
Why wasn't the entire kingdom ripped
away from Solomon and his family?

10:56.605 --> 10:58.404
Because of David.

10:58.406 --> 11:00.941
As far as he was concerned,
there was no other relationship

11:00.943 --> 11:04.076
