and disastrous decision.</i>

11:28.971 --> 11:30.037
And so, this morning's sermon

11:30.039 --> 11:32.272
is intended as an encouragement
to those of you

11:32.274 --> 11:35.407
who take your relationship
with God seriously.

11:35.409 --> 11:36.976
