12:08.276 --> 12:09.375
Which brings us sadly

12:09.377 --> 12:12.244
to the tragic story
this week

12:12.246 --> 12:15.215
of our own young
Megan Lancaster,

12:15.217 --> 12:19.185
who saw a deer that had
been injured at East Point.

12:19.187 --> 12:21.955
As was her nature, she ran
to help the stricken animal

12:21.957 --> 12:23.592
and in so doing,

12:24.525 --> 12:25.895
fell from the cliff.

12:28.362 --> 12:30.931
How sad so young a person
should lose her life

12:30.933 --> 12:33.302
in coming to the aid
of a lowly animal.

12:34.970 --> 12:37.403
And yet the difference
between a person and an animal

12:37.405 --> 12:38.939
is no greater
than the difference

12:38.941 --> 12:40.676
